      <title>英國駁回伊朗在襲擊以色列之前發出警告的說法</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-dismisses-iran-assertion-it-gave-warning-before-attacking-israel-2024-04-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英國首相里希·蘇納克的發言人週一表示，英國否認伊朗聲稱在襲擊以色列之前提前通知的說法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-dismisses-iran-assertion-it-gave-warning-before-attacking-israel-2024-04-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 11:54:41 GMT</pubDate>
