      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/azerbaijan-asks-world-court-throw-out-armenian-ethnic-cleansing-case-2024-04-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿塞拜疆週一要求聯合國最高法院駁回其高加索鄰國亞美尼亞提起的案件，該案件指控其種族清洗並違反聯合國反歧視條約。]]></description>
